Description: A modernized fork of the original SIndexR package that exposes
  site index routines for practical forestry workflows in R. This package
  adds consistent wrapper APIs, external DLL backend support, legacy
  compatibility guidance, and end-to-end examples for Permanent Sample Plot
  (PSP) and growth-and-yield treelist preparation.
